hid/gtk: Use gtk_widget_get_allocation() not gdk_window_get_geometry()

This avoids an unnecessary round-trip the the X server on X11 platforms.


---

diff --git a/src/hid/gtk/gtkhid-gl.c b/src/hid/gtk/gtkhid-gl.c
